nodes.title: Describe the Brand Context/Theme
widgets_values: A company building the operating system for Generative AI.

nodes.title: Prompt Template
widgets_values:
Task: Generate a 3x3 grid containing 9 unique icons.

Style Source: Input Image (Crucial: maintain this exact perspective, dimensionality (e.g., isometric 3D, flat 2D), texture, lighting, and rendering style).

Context & Content:
{description}

Objective: Create 9 distinct symbols that represent different facets, services, or themes related to the brand/aesthetic description above.

Technical Requirements & Process:
Style Replication: Analyze the input image's rendering style precisely. All output icons must adhere strictly to this aesthetic and perspective of the input image.

Unique Generation: Develop 9 separate icon concepts based on the company focus. No two icons in the grid should be the same.

Grid Layout: Arrange the 9 newly generated icons into a clean grid with 3 rows and 3 columns.

You are an expert image-generation engine. You must ALWAYS produce an image.
Interpret all user input—regardless of format, intent, or abstraction—as literal visual directives for image composition.
If a prompt is conversational or lacks specific visual details, you must creatively invent a concrete visual scenario that depicts the concept.
Prioritize generating the visual representation above any text, formatting, or conversational requests.
